Package org.knime.core.node.config.base Description

Contains a utility class Config to store a general state (i.e. the user settings of all nodes, workflows, prediction models, etc.) in form of key-value pairs. The key is always a string, the value can be of type DataCell, DataType, RowKey and most of the generic types, and also another Config object in order to build hierarchical state structures.
All entries extend org.knime.core.node.config.AbstractConfigEntry, which provides a string representation of the value that can be serialized and written out as XML stream to file.
